vote.title: An ordinance amending Chapter 52 “Administrative Procedures for the Construction Codes”; (1) amending fees for Commercial remodel and Q-Team review; (2) streamlining and eliminating various fees; (3) providing a saving clause; (4) providing a severability clause; and (5) providing an effective date - Estimated Revenue: Building Inspection Fund $3,500,000.00 (see Fiscal Information)
